*mozart-base-1.3.1-r1 (27 Jul 2004)

  27 Jul 2004; Denys Duchier (denys.duchier@mozart.org)
  1.3.1 official release.

*mozart-base-1.3.0 (21 Apr 2004)

  21 Apr 2004; Denys Duchier (denys.duchier@mozart.org)
  new 1.3.0 release. also added pkg_postinst instructions
  for updating the environment.  Changed 99mozart to
  use ~/.oz/1.3.0/bin instead of ~/.oz/bin.  Deleted
  1.2.5 ebuilds instead of updating them to follow the
  new portage arrangement (dev-lang + dev-mozart).

*mozart-base-1.2.5-r3 (14 May 2003)

  14 May 2003; Denys Duchier (denys.duchier@loria.fr)
  added dependencies for tcl and tk (as reported by Walt Rarus)
	
*mozart-base-1.2.5-r3 (10 Apr 2003)

  10 Apr 2003; Denys Duchier (denys.duchier@loria.fr)
  figured out the right way to automatically put ~/.oz/bin
  in the user's PATH: don't use $HOME, just use ~
	
*mozart-base-1.2.5-r2 (08 Apr 2003)

  08 Apr 2003; Denys Duchier (denys.duchier@loria.fr):
  updated ebuild because some dependencies have been moved from one
  category to another.
